that any person on Friday after namaz’e Subh recites YAA FATTAA-HO 77 times and mean while look to his chest than the rust of negligence will be away from him and his heart will be clear and pure, his problems will automatically solve.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh jo shakhs Juma ke din Namaz’e Subh ke baad 77 martaba YAA FATTAA-HO ka vird kare aur us dauraan apni nigaahe’n apne seene (chest) ki taraf dekhe to us ke seene se ghaflat ka zang (rust) dur ho jaayega aur us ka dil paak o saaf ho jaayega, uski mushkilaat khud ba khud khatm ho jaayegi.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جو شخص جمعہ کے روز نماز صبح کے بعد 77 مرتبہ ’’یَافَتَّاحُ‘‘  کا ورد کرے اور اس دوران اپنی نگاہیں اپنے سینہ پر مرکوز رکھے تو اس کے سینہ سے غفلت کا زنگ دور ہوجائے گا اور اس کا دل پاک و صاف ہوجائے گا اس کی مشکلات خودبخود ختم ہوجائیں گی۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020835, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "If a person recites YAA FATTAA-HO 1793 times for 18 days and nights than he will be aware of the hidden secrets, his inner will be clean, if he desires to be a ruler he will achieve great success. Do remember that if the wishes are fulfilled then he should recite YAA FATTAA-HO at least 500 times daily.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar koi shakhs 18 raat o din rozaana 1793 martaba YAA FATTAA-HO ka vird kare to us ke liye ghaib ki baate’n zaahir hone lagengi, us ka baatin (androoni) saaf ho jaayega, agar us ki muraad dunya mein hukm-raani hongi to usey fateh azeem haasil hogi. Yaad rahe keh jo bhi is amal ke zariye apni haajaat paale’n to laazmi hai keh YAA FATTAA-HO ka vird rozaana kam az kam 500 martaba zaroor kiya kare.", "UrduDescription": "اگر کوئی شخص 18 شب و روز روزانہ 1793 مرتبہ ’’یَافَتَّاحُ‘‘  کا ورد کرے تو اس کے لئے غیب کی باتیں ظاہر ہونے لگیں گی، اس کا باطن صاف ہوجائے گا، اگر اس کی مراد دنیا میں حکمرانی ہوگی تو اسے فتح عظیم حاصل ہوگی۔ یاد رہے جو بھی اس عمل کے ذریعے اپنی حاجات پالیں تو لازمی ہے کہ اس اسم کا ورد روزانہ کم از کم 500 مرتبہ ضرور کیا کریں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBl